{
  "stem": "21648.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So really and truly, I had to close my store, because there was no business.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Communists have [INAUDIBLE] business.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I have to close the store, but we had enough food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We wasn't starving, let's put it this way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Was your husband still able to do his business?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, nobody was doing nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was working in-- [? by-- ?] the Russian in a warehouse for food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we was Polish, Polish citizen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For the Russian?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hitler came, and then that was the end of our life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Well, what they did-- the first thing was start to hide the husbands, the men, because they was killing the men.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were saying they-- they Communist, they-- they fight for them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had a barn in the back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And often the family, my father-in-law, my brother-in-laws, my husband, all those, they-- they was in the barn hiding.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was the provider to cook and bring-- bring them the food and everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And how about your daughter?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What were you doing with your daughter?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My daughter was in my hands.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was my [? saver. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was not right. ?] She was three years old, so where I went I was carrying my daughter with me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then Rosh Hashanah, when we had-- you know, have to daven.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know what a Torah is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I went to the synagogue, and I took out the Torah and I took the [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Ukraine ?] shawl.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so-- and I covered like a child and I brought into the barn.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the man was there praying, davening, praying to God.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "God should save us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was that, but my daughter never came off my lap, my hands.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
